    "1VQ6AQ": {
        "en-US": "[Song Mudoo]\nOh, is that so.\nWell, can’t be helped.\nSee you next time.",
        "pt-BR": "[Song Mudoo]\nAh, entendi.\nBom, fazer o quê.\nAté a próxima.",
